+ Monitor and Optimize\nAuto Loader Streams
++ cloud_files_state()
+++_ SQL function: query file state
+++_ Input: checkpoint path
+++_ Shows discovered files + status
++ Streaming Metrics
+++_ numFilesOutstanding: pending files
+++_ numBytesOutstanding: pending bytes
+++_ Visible in Streaming progress dashboard
-- Rate Limiting
---_ cloudFiles.maxFilesPerTrigger
---_ cloudFiles.maxBytesPerTrigger
---_ Prevents oversized micro-batches
-- File Metadata
---_ _metadata hidden column
---_ file_path, file_name, file_size
---_ file_modification_time
---_ Useful for auditing and lineage
